{"error":0,"message":"","data":[{"show_ID":"2147","airdate":"1549393200","name_switch":"off","DJ":"ziona and Slaygon","showname":"Free-flow Show","blurb":"Hi Everyone! \n\nWe are back after we defeated the evil Deadly Man Flu\u2122, and this time there are no rules for requesting songs - request whatever you feel like! Random SIDs are also welcome again :) \nLet's kick-start this month with some good vibes! \n\nJoin us and SLAY tuned.","nice_showname":"<strong><big>ziona and Slaygon<\/big><\/strong><br \/>Free-flow Show","nice_airdate":"Tuesday 5th February, 2019<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"2146","airdate":"1549789200","name_switch":"off","DJ":"Gazoo","showname":"PmpVsBionicBoots","blurb":"I'm going to talk a bit about bionic boots and how a video about them is making me sad.\n\nThen I'm also going to talk a bit more about the Fyre festival.\n\nYou will either listen, watch, both, or neither. The choice is yours!\n\nGazoo","nice_showname":"<strong><big>Gazoo<\/big><\/strong><br \/>PmpVsBionicBoots","nice_airdate":"Sunday 10th February, 2019<br \/>at 10:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"2145","airdate":"1550422800","name_switch":"off","DJ":"Remix64.com","showname":"Remixer of the Year Awards 2018","blurb":"The time has come to celebrate and acknowledge the remixers' work in the C64 and Amiga community by presenting the yearly ROTY Awards, as voted by the users at www.remix64.com. This year it's SLAY Radio's turn to give out the awards and give you a run-down of what happened in 2018.","nice_showname":"<strong><big>Remix64.com<\/big><\/strong><br \/>Remixer of the Year Awards 2018","nice_airdate":"Sunday 17th February, 2019<br \/>at 18:00 USRT"}]}